blogs.title: My Code wars routine
blogs.body: Do them daily, at least one. Its good practice, to gain programmer thinking. It also help me to train my Deep Work and habits forming

blogs.title: Read at leas chapter a day
blogs.body: Currently im on `Atomic Habits` by James Clear. It shows how developing habits can change life by changing at least 1% a day. Also provides a lot of great examples, and tasks.
